 result\n$\\xi (\\beta_1\\ll 1)\\simeq (r+2)/(r-1)$, whereas for ultrarelativistic\n($\\Gamma_1\\gg 1$) shock speeds the spectral index value is close to unity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2015 17:20:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-19"}
